headline: Reassessing T-Mobile US (TMUS) After Recent Share Price Weakness
summary: If you are wondering whether T-Mobile US at around US$185 per share is starting to look like value, or if the easier gains may already have occurred, this article is for you. The stock is currently around US$185.39, with returns of a 2.8% decline over 7 days, a 6.2% decline over 30 days, a 7.1% decline year to date, a 12.8% decline over 1 year, while still showing 29.1% over 3 years and 50.2% over 5 years. Recent share price moves are being viewed in the context of ongoing industry...

headline: Personal bios for customer service agents can boost satisfaction
